<div class="backgroundcolor">
<div class="hero-wrapper">

  <div class="hero-content container text-center">

    <h1 class="hero-title">Mobile Sports Massage in London</h1>

    <p class="hero-subtitle">
      Expert massage therapy delivered to your door.
    </p>

    <ul class="greentick">
      <li>Appointments 10am–10pm</li>
      <li>Qualified, vetted and insured</li>
      <li>Clinical and evidence-based approach</li>
    </ul>

    <a href="#booking" class="btn btn-light btn-lg mt-3">
      Book Your Treatment
    </a>

  </div>

  <!-- Trust Bar -->
  <div class="trust-bar">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row text-center">

        <div class="col-md-3 col-6">
          <div class="trust-item">
            <h6>University Qualified</h6>
            <p>Sports Therapy Degree</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-3 col-6">
          <div class="trust-item">
            <h6>Fully Insured</h6>
            <p>Professional Cover</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-3 col-6">
          <div class="trust-item">
            <h6>Mobile Service</h6>
            <p>Treatments at Your Home</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-3 col-6">
          <div class="trust-item">
            <h6>5★ Client Reviews</h6>
            <p>Trusted by Local Clients</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

  <section class="about-section">
  <div class="about-wrapper">

    <div class="about-image">
      <%= cl_image_tag("ChatGPT_Image_Mar_4_2026_09_50_41_AM_ukiglj", class: "about-image-cover") %>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <h2 class="about-name">About Tom</h2>
      <p class="about-role">Sports Therapist</p>

      <div class="about-divider"></div>

      <p class="about-text">
       I’ve spent the past 16 years helping people move better, recover from injury, and perform at their best. My clients have ranged from professional athletes and public figures to busy professionals balancing demanding work and family life.<br><br>

       <button class="btn btn-outline-dark" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#aboutTomModal">
         Read more about Tom
        </button>
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
  <div class="container">
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-center">Treatments</h2>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="row justify-content-center g-4">
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-5 d-flex">
          <div class="card w-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <%=cl_image_tag("therapeuticmassage_hemrkx", class: "card-img-top", alt: "Theraputic massage image")  %>
              <h3 class="card-title">Theraputic Massage</h3>
              <h5><b>Restore balance. Reset the nervous system.</b></h5>
              <p>A deeply calming treatment designed to reduce accumulated stress and encourage full-body relaxation.</p>
              <h4 class="card-title">Benefits</h4>
              <ul>
               <li>Reduces accumulated stress and sympathetic overdrive</li>
               <li>Relieves general muscular tension from daily strain</li>
               <li>Improves sleep quality and recovery capacity</li>
               <li>Enhances circulation and tissue nourishment</li>
               <li>Supports mental clarity and emotional regulation</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-5 d-flex">
          <div class="card w-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <%=cl_image_tag("sports-massage-deep-tissue_ziu36h", class: "card-img-top", alt: "Deep tissue massage image")  %>
              <h3 class="card-title">Deep Tissue Massage</h3>
              <h5><b>Targeted treatment for chronic tension.</b></h5>
              <p>A focused, slower-paced approach that works into deeper muscle layers to address persistent tightness and restriction.</p>
              <h4 class="card-title">Benefits</h4>
               <ul>
                 <li>Releases chronic muscular tension</li>
                 <li>Improves mobility and joint range of motion</li>
                 <li>Reduces long-standing neck, shoulder and lower back discomfort</li>
                 <li>Breaks down adhesions and areas of restriction</li>
                 <li>Supports recovery from repetitive strain patterns</li>
             </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-5 d-flex">
          <div class="card w-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <%=cl_image_tag("sprtmss_vaqdxe", class: "card-img-top", alt: "Sport massage image")  %>
              <h3 class="card-title">Sports Massage</h3>
              <h5><b>Performance-driven, clinically informed treatment.</b></h5>
              <p>Designed for active and sedentary individuals who want to move better, recover faster and reduce injury risk.</p>
              <h4 class="card-title">Benefits</h4>
              <ul>
                 <li>Supports injury prevention strategies</li>
                 <li>Assists rehabilitation of minor strains and overuse issues</li>
                 <li>Improves movement efficiency and flexibility</li>
                 <li>Reduces post-training soreness and recovery time</li>
                 <li>Identifies and addresses muscular imbalances</li>
             </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-5 d-flex">
          <div class="card w-100">
            <div class="card-body  d-flex flex-column">
              <%=cl_image_tag("CuppingTherapy_uimjvb", class: "card-img-top", alt: "Cupping massage image")  %>
              <h3 class="card-title">Cupping Massage</h3>
              <h5><b>Advanced myofascial decompression.</b></h5>
              <p>A specialised technique used to lift and decompress soft tissue, increasing local circulation and reducing fascial restriction.</p>
              <h4 class="card-title">Benefits</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Increases local blood flow to targeted areas</li>
                <li>Reduces deep muscular tightness</li>
                <li>Releases fascial restriction</li>
                <li>Supports tissue recovery and mobility</li>
                <li>Complements deep tissue and sports massage</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container py-5">

  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-lg-7">

      <div class="text-center mb-4">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-muted">Have a question or want to book a treatment? Get in touch.</p>

        <p class="mb-1">
          <strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:07123456789">07123 456789</a>
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@thelondonmassage.co.uk">info@thelondonmassage.co.uk</a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card2 shadow-sm border-0">
        <div class="card-body pt-4 pb-2 px-4">

          <h4 class="mb-4 text-center">Send a Message</h4>

          <%= form_with url: contact_path, method: :post do |f| %>

            <div class="mb-3">
              <%= f.label :name, class: "form-label fw-semibold" %>
              <%= f.text_field :name, class: "form-control form-control-lg", placeholder: "Your name", required: true %>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-3">
              <%= f.label :email, class: "form-label fw-semibold" %>
              <%= f.email_field :email, class: "form-control form-control-lg", placeholder: "your@email.com", required: true %>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-3">
              <%= f.label :phone, "Telephone", class: "form-label fw-semibold" %>
              <%= f.telephone_field :phone, class: "form-control", placeholder: "07...", required: true %>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-3">
              <%= f.label :address, "Address / Location", class: "form-label fw-semibold" %>
              <%= f.text_field :address, class: "form-control", placeholder: "Where the treatment will take place", required: true %>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-4">
              <%= f.label :message, class: "form-label fw-semibold" %>
              <%= f.text_area :message, class: "form-control", rows: 5, placeholder: "How can I help?", required: true %>
            </div>

            <div class="d-grid pb-4">
              <%= f.submit "Send Message", class: "btn btn-dark btn-lg" %>
            </div>

          <% end %>

        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="modal fade" id="aboutTomModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="aboutTomModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg modal-dialog-centered">
    <div class="modal-content">

      <div class="modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title" id="aboutTomModalLabel">About Tom Elsom</h5>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
      </div>

      <div class="modal-body">

        <p>
        I’ve spent the past 16 years helping people move better, recover from injury,
        and perform at their best. My clients have ranged from professional athletes
        and public figures to busy professionals balancing demanding work and family life.
        </p>

        <p>
        Over the years I’ve seen how modern lifestyles place constant strain on the body.
        Long hours at desks, repetitive movement, training loads, and everyday stress can
        all lead to pain, tension, and reduced mobility.
        </p>

        <p>
        My treatments focus on identifying the underlying causes of discomfort and
        addressing them with targeted hands-on therapy. Sessions may combine sports
        massage, deep tissue techniques, and remedial work to restore movement and
        reduce pain.
        </p>

        <p>
        Now based in South London, I offer professional treatments in the comfort of
        your home. Each session is tailored to the individual, combining therapy with
        practical advice where needed so improvements continue beyond the treatment.
        </p>

        <p><strong>The aim is simple: lasting results and helping you move through life with less pain.</strong></p>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
